metadata.name: #14/50 Dr. Temple Grandin
metadata.description:
14/50 Dr. Temple Grandin

This is Lil' Legend Dr. Temple Grandin. She has autism and thinks in pictures like me! Dr. Temple Grandin is an inspiring autism advocate, she is smart and feels pretty cool!

Artwork info:
Dr. Temple Grandin is a hand made, baked/hardened polymer clay character.

Shipping & Collector info:

Dr. Temple Grandin will be shipped to collector with a display case!

Hold 3+ Lil' Legends NFTs and receive a free custom made character by Nadia.
